text: Jonathan Wolff (born October 23, 1958 in Louisville, Kentucky) is an American composer. ==Biography== Wolff is well known for creating the theme and music for the television series Seinfeld. Wolff is also the composer for about 75 other TV series, including Will & Grace, Who's the Boss?, Married... with Children, The Hughleys, and Reba. ==References== ==External links== * * Jonathan Wolff, Public Speaker * Category:American television composers Category:Living people Category:Musicians from Louisville, Kentucky Category:1958 births Category:Atherton High School alumni
